Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to blame yourself. You're only human, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We let them escape, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems as though we have a bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm gonna start filming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scene where the heroine finds out about her lover's death, take five!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One week?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it bad for the leader to be gone that long?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some matters can't be settled unless I go in person.{lol talking to leader of funeral parlor in the middle of school}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behave yourself and enjoy school for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, I'll be a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not true. I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut, cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu's just different lately, somehow. Bolder, or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's like a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe something happened in Oshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A vacation on a southern island! A summer love affair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so the young man climbs the stairway to adulthood!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life really doesn't go the way we want it to, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about Yahiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even went to the orphanage, but they say he hasn't visited.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We used to play there together all the time as kids, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm looking for is at the aquarium?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not looking for a fish, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, "Your lucky item of love is a tiger-striped tea kettle."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Where are you supposed to find {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tiger-striped tea kettle.{what the actual fuck.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, so you two haven't gone home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this yours, Ouma?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Souta's using it for the film. It's the lover's... memento, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, he says he's gonna have Inori hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot something in the club room!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go deliver this for you, so you go shopping with Hare for me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai— Kanon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your lucky chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it! Lucky chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does she mean, "lucky chance"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told there's a ghost about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:05:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone entered the Oshima lab with Dr. Ouma Kurosu's ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Keido Shuichiro, you were once close colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you offer any explanation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Sir, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we getting off? For your shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you have lots of bags?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Yeah, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll be able to carry them all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hare... are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:06:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oho, having a little fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Yahiro, this is just—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahiro. Is that all you have to say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to say? You want to air everything out right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hare, I need you to go shopping by yourself, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to talk with Yahiro about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouma Shu. Keeping an eye on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was clearly the right call.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They told me they were going to put Jun down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we took advantage of the confusion and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I couldn't let him stay there any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sold you out to get us into that place,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and in the end I ran away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you fall again? Do you hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've acquired the fugitive Cancerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah! Nice guts!{best character}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really need my Endlave for a simple little Cancerous hunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what they say, a dragon goes full force even against a slime!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a dragon would seriously eat a slime...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that, Scarface?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Dan! Leave the rest to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll clear this mission with guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called "knowing how to get ahead."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you lend me some money?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need money to run and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you went out of your way to show Jun to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Shu. I'm the only one left who can protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Gai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left already, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have someone I want you to harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's an Apocalypse patient. The Carcinogenesis has started already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to talk to Shibungi, and then we'll give you the ord—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading to Point Yellow-One now.  Pick us up there in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't mean I've forgiven you for what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jun hasn't done anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look it over. We'll have to use this very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This song is wrong now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Jun. Bear with it for just a little while, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they've finally come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready for gene capture?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The system check is done. But why use something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it wrong to want to get to know the person you're in love with?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anti Bodies?! How have they found us already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw this coming. For now, just move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A terrorist attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D'ya think the Undertakers are back or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's use {\i1}that{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has to be a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Opening up an escape route and luring in the enemy is a basic tactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep thinking like an amateur, you're going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just try to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a Void on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the power to draw poeple's hearts out as weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can even take down an Endlave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me to believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you're not the one who called in those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hypocrite.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't betray people like you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't abandon them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll make sure Jun escapes, just like I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you have to do is shut up and let me use you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry. Your big brother's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You again, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You faceless bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jun, I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But today, I've got something special!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing will follow that light.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad. How about some continuous fire, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Segai! What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is unexpected, but I must say it's intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That object and the Apocalypse Cancer displayed the same reading...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It migrated?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jun, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can I ever explain this to Yahiro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the Apocalypse Virus cause genomic resonance in the machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the one there is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reboot PINs! I'll input every last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Segai, you're in danger! Please move away from the action!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll withdraw for now. Abort the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... Roppongi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From before Lost Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... Jun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally get to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a one-time deal, got it? Just for your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is December 24th, 2029.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the happiest time of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:17:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost Christmas is about to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be on my way now, and just take this one happy memory with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu... please use that Void to cut off my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother's Void is the Void that severs life.{sure is mystic shears of death perception}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Void to lay my body to rest with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crystals that stole my freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,gave me the ability to see Voids in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I saw there was another big brother besides the one he showed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat pizza today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll order you the tomato one you like, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the way. You're in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen unkind sides to kind people over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends, ladies in our family, people from the health center...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're probably the same, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I live any longer, this sadness will hit me again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll end up hating my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go out as the me who loves my wonderful big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay; your big brother is here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:18:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever. I'll be here for you forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! At this rate, I'll end up killing my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother... was it a nuisance having me around?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I wreck your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hate me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, here's how I feel about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life doesn't go the way we want it to, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right— Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Jun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu...
